data.description: This is a MUST SEE in the desirable Lakewood neighborhood of Norfolk! This beautiful, all brick ranch is ready for your to call it home! Situated on a corner lot, this spacious 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath has all the space you are looking for! Features include a very modern & open floor plan, updated kitchen with granite countertops, breakfast nook and huge living room to gather and entertain in! Sip your morning coffee on your custom front patio, and entertain in your fully fenced back yard!  Large driveway and attached garage for all your vehicles. Located  directly across from a city owned open space. Super convenient to shopping, dining, Military Bases and Shipyard with easy access to interstates connecting you to anywhere in Hampton Roads. No HOA! Call your agent today for your own personal tour and see why people love Lakewood!
